OL,3,CRoyal Mail fined #21m by watchdog for
OL,4,Cfailing to meet delivery targets
OL,6,FRoyal Mail has been fined #21 million
OL,7,Ffor missing its first and second class
OL,8,Fmail delivery targets in the 2024-25
OL,9,Ffinancial year, regulator Ofcom said.
OL,11,FIt represents the third-largest fine
OL,12,Fever imposed by the communications
OL,13,Fwatchdog.
OL,15,FThe delivery giant delivered 77% of
OL,16,Ffirst-class mail and 92.5% of second-
OL,17,Fclass mail on time during the 2024-25
OL,18,Ffinancial year, Ofcom found.
OL,20,FThis was short of its respective 93%
OL,21,Fand 98.5% targets.
