OL,3,CRoyal Mail fined #21m by watchdog for
OL,4,Cfailing to meet delivery targets
OL,6,FIan Strawhorne, director of
OL,7,Fenforcement at Ofcom, said: "Millions
OL,8,Fof important letters are arriving
OL,9,Flate, and people aren't getting what
OL,10,Fthey pay for when they buy a stamp.
OL,12,F"These persistent failures are
OL,13,Funacceptable, and customers expect and
OL,14,Fdeserve better.
OL,16,F"Royal Mail must rebuild consumers'
OL,17,Fconfidence as a matter of urgency. And
OL,18,Fthat means making actual significant
OL,19,Fimprovements, not more empty promises."
